column1: # TO BE USED TO INSERT MODEL ANNOTATIONS IN METABOLIC ATLAS DATABASE
# annotations will be visible in the GEM browser pages and some can be used by the search engine
# this is a TAB separated file, thus TABs are not allowed in any field values
# each line added must have exactly 7 columns to be parsed properly
# column 'id' is mandatory, other columns are optional
# name               | primary name/symbol of the gene
# alternate_name     | long name or full name of the gene
# aliases            | list of aliases, semi-colon separated values
# function           | text about the function, can describe multiple functions
# ec                 | EC code, semi-colon separated values
# catalytic_activity | text about the catalytic activity
